Stack

App:            Go 1.22 + Gin — /metrics (Golden Signals: RED), /health, Swagger UI
Infra:          Terraform — VPC, EKS 1.31, Karpenter (Spot+OD), ECR, S3
CI/CD:          Jenkins (in-cluster, JCasC, Multibranch) → ArgoCD (GitOps, App-of-Apps)
Banco:          CloudNativePG — 3 instâncias HA, backup S3, ServiceMonitor
Observability:  kube-prometheus-stack — Prometheus, Grafana (RED dashboard), AlertManager
Secrets:        Bitnami SealedSecrets — criptografados no Git
Ingress:        AWS ALB Controller
Segurança:      golangci-lint, govulncheck, OWASP ZAP, Trivy (image scan), SonarQube
